overview: Invicta FC 31: Jandiroba vs. Morandin is an upcoming mixed martial arts event to be headlined by Virna Jandiroba defending her strawweight championship against Janaisa Morandin. The bout was originally scheduled to headline Invicta 28 before Morandin pulled out due to injury.
title: Invicta FC 31: Jandiroba vs. Morandin
